-- Chad Signs 12 Million-Euro Accord With France for Water Project
-- B y   D a n i e l   N ’ D o h   N a d j i t a n
-- 2013-06-24T11:58:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-06-24/chad-signs-12-million-euro-accord-with-france-for-water-project.html
Chad’s government signed a 12
million-euro ($16 million) agreement with France for a water
project in the capital, Ndjamena, the French Development Agency
said.  The accord will promote access to safe drinking water and
sanitation in eastern neighborhoods of the city, Jean-Marc
Pradelle, director of the agency’s mission in Chad, told
reporters today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ndoh Nadjitan in N’Djamena at 
 nnadjitan@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
